    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone prioritizing utility. While the engine and transmission are fully operational, the car shows clear signs of its age, including some minor fluid seepage and noticeable cosmetic wear on both the interior and exterior. It has been maintained to stay roadworthy, though a new owner should expect to address some typical high-mileage maintenance items in the future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable, functional vehicle that still has life left in it.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
